sequenceDiagram
    actor 사용자
    participant UI as 웹 UI
    participant Ctrl as VersionControl
    participant Perm as SharePermission
    participant Ver as FileVersion
    participant Storage as StorageService
    participant DB as Database
    participant Log as ActivityLog

    사용자->>UI: 복구할 버전 선택
    UI->>Ctrl: restoreVersion(fileId, versionId, userId)
    Ctrl->>Perm: verifyModify(userId, fileId)
    Perm-->>Ctrl: 권한 확인 결과
    Ctrl->>Ver: restore(versionId)
    Ver->>DB: find(versionId)
    Ver->>Storage: loadFile(storagePath)
    Ver->>DB: update(currentVersion)
    Ctrl->>Log: record(VERSION_RESTORE)
    Ctrl-->>UI: 복구 완료 응답
    UI-->>사용자: 복구 결과 표시
